  "markup": "\u003Cp\u003EDifferential diagnosis of the human shoulder can difficult at times; conditions can overlap and sometimes confound even the best clinicians.\u0026nbsp; Once your diagnosis has been rendered, the question of how to treat has to be addressed. Super Pulsed Laser provides a new range of treatment options that offer superior results.\u0026nbsp; Learn all about the conditions that can affect the shoulder, and learn how to incorporate low-level laser to treat these conditions.\u003C/p\u003E"
}]]></Value>
